<sect1 id="dir_ec78eb07ca45680dda148d5b3c7a447e_1autotoc_md131">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::spawn</title><para>Entity spawning and lifecycle management.</para>
<para>This module provides the infrastructure for spawning and despawning GameObjects at runtime based on configurable conditions and strategies.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_ec78eb07ca45680dda148d5b3c7a447e_1autotoc_md132">
<title>Architecture</title><para>The spawn system follows a command-based architecture with separation of concerns:</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">┌─────────────────────┐<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>┌─────────────────────┐</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>SpawnCondition<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/><sp/>SpawnStrategy<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/>(when<sp/>to<sp/>spawn)<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/><sp/>(how<sp/>to<sp/>spawn)<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">└─────────┬───────────┘<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>└──────────┬──────────┘</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>▼<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>▼</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>GameObjectSpawnSystem<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/>(calculates<sp/>budget,<sp/>emits<sp/>SpawnCommands)<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────┘</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>▼</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>SpawnCommandDispatcher<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/>(routes<sp/>commands<sp/>to<sp/>SpawnManager)<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">└─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────┘</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>▼</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>SpawnManager<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">│<sp/><sp/><sp/>(acquires<sp/>from<sp/>pool,<sp/>applies<sp/>strategy)<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_ec78eb07ca45680dda148d5b3c7a447e_1autotoc_md133">
